name: #smol Square Skull III - DoL (#smoldol)
description: @DolCreative - Third in the series of #smol Square Skulls, this one is a tribute to the neo-expressionist portraiture style that typically heavily influences the artist. As the text usually found heavily in such a style is not easily translated to 10x10px it is instead featured via a 1x1px flashing morse code signature, spelling D O L. GIF spanning 27 frames.
